Sterling Capital Management LLC Key Developments

Vanguard Explorer Value Fund Announces Departure of Sterling Capital Management LLC as Advisor
Jun 6 16
Vanguard announced modifications to the investment advisory arrangements of the $317 million Explorer Value Fund (VEVFX). Sterling Capital Management LLC will no longer serve as an advisor to the fund. The portion of the portfolio formerly managed by Sterling (approximately 31% of fund assets) has been equally apportioned to existing managers Frontier Capital Management Co., LLC and Cardinal Capital Management, L.L.C.


